  "comment": "Outshine Q500 is an IP65 sleek modern unit equipped with 48 10W RGBW LEDs that can illuminate a variety of indoor and outdoor settings. It has the ability to create countless color combinations with even coverage and a compelling color balance due to its 16 Bit dimming. The colors are hyphenated by the two segment mode that multiplies each color and enables the ability to create an assortment of various color combinations and profound saturates as well as warm pastels and exquisite crisp hues and tints. It is supplied with Wireless Solutions WDMX and can be accessorized with a removable barn door and diffusion filter for further control of the light. The Outshine Q500 creates a clean wash effect, smooth color mixing transitions and generate vibrant colors that can transform any venue.",
